  <brief_title>Open-label Crossover Metformin Gum Versus Tablet in Healthy Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open-label,Randomized, Crossover Study Comparing Metformin Gum and Immediate Release Tablet in Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
