  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Single-dose, randomized, open-label, cross over study. The study will have an open-label, 3
      period, 3 treatments, and randomized design.

      Each volunteer will receive a Metformin gum 2x250mg, Metformin gum 1x250mg &amp; Metformin tablet
      500mg
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
