  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To determine the difference in the pharmacokinetic profile of metformin following administration of two formulations (gum and tablet).</measure>
    <time_frame>45 days</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>To evaluate the effect on blood glucose levels as well as safety and tolerability of one time administration of the Metformin Gum and Metformin tablet.</measure>
